### Create a guest booking
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/guest-booking
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "phone": "+353871234567",
  "barberId": 1,
  "serviceId": 1,
  "bookingDate": "2025-11-20",
  "startTime": "10:00:00",
  "paymentMethod": "pay_online",
  "notes": "First time customer"
}

### Save guest account (convert to registered user)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/save-account
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "password": "SecurePassword123"
}

### Login with saved guest account
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "john.doe@example.com",
  "password": "SecurePassword123"
}

